### SurveyResultController API Tests for Survey Answers
### Base URL
@baseUrl = https://localhost:7001
@contentType = application/json

### Variables
@userId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
@surveyId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
@surveyResultId = REPLACE_WITH_ACTUAL_ID
@questionId1 = REPLACE_WITH_Q1_ID
@questionId2 = REPLACE_WITH_Q2_ID
@questionId3 = REPLACE_WITH_Q3_ID

### 1. Submit Answers for "Customer Satisfaction Survey"
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/SurveyResult
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "surveyId": "{{surveyId}}",
  "datePassed": "2025-10-08T10:00:00Z",
  "answers": [
    { 
      "questionId": "{{questionId1}}",
      "questionTitle": "How satisfied are you with our service?",
      "values": ["Very satisfied"]
    },
    { 
      "questionId": "{{questionId2}}",
      "questionTitle": "What is your preferred contact method?",
      "values": ["email"]
    },
    { 
      "questionId": "{{questionId3}}",
      "questionTitle": "Which features do you use?",
      "values": ["mobile","web"]
    }
  ]
}

###

### 2. Update Survey Result (Replace surveyResultId with actual ID)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/SurveyResult
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "id": "{{surveyResultId}}",
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "surveyId": "{{surveyId}}",
  "datePassed": "2025-10-08T12:00:00Z",
  "answers": [
    { 
      "questionId": "{{questionId1}}",
      "questionTitle": "How satisfied are you with our updated service?",
      "values": ["Satisfied"]
    }
  ]
}
